{"tid":1059934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子新西蘭墮海　牛仔褲打結充救生衣獲救","createTime":"2019-03-13T12:24:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T08:13:06.000Z","uid":86509,"like":382,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"1a6c96ec6d5ec8c45176cd73ffcaa743bebf4db0","tid":1059934,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T12:24:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20190312/s00005/1552383609037/【短片】男子新西蘭墮海-牛仔褲打結充救生衣獲救\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20190312%2Fs00005%2F1552383609037%2F%E3%80%90%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87%E3%80%91%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E6%96%B0%E8%A5%BF%E8%98%AD%E5%A2%AE%E6%B5%B7-%E7%89%9B%E4%BB%94%E8%A4%B2%E6%89%93%E7%B5%90%E5%85%85%E6%95%91%E7%94%9F%E8%A1%A3%E7%8D%B2%E6%95%91&d=WTugOjWmLb2R3dS25JBA%2BdTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=27cffa6f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20190312%2Fs00005%2F1552383609037%2F%E3%80%90%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87%E3%80%91%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E6%96%B0%E8%A5%BF%E8%98%AD%E5%A2%AE%E6%B5%B7-%E7%89%9B%E4%BB%94%E8%A4%B2%E6%89%93%E7%B5%90%E5%85%85%E6%95%91%E7%94%9F%E8%A1%A3%E7%8D%B2%E6%95%91&h=38d88a87\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20190312/s00005/1552383609037/【短片】男子新西蘭墮海-牛仔褲打結充救生衣獲救</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3yGBWCN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3yGBWCN.jpg&h=f5772fa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一名男子上周在新西蘭外海不慎掉出船外，身上無穿救生衣，而且愈飄愈遠。他急中生智脫下牛仔褲把褲腳打結充氣，變成「臨時救生衣」，漂浮3個多小時後終於等到救援直升機出現。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n30歲的德國籍男子莫克（Arne Murke）與弟弟接下一筆生意，上周三（6日）負責把一艘12米長的帆船，由新西蘭運到巴西交貨。當船航行到距離新西蘭托拉加灣約28公里外時，主帆索突然鬆脫，船桁打轉時把莫克打進海中，當時他手臂被繩索纏住，一度被壓在船身下，幸好掙脫。船上的兄弟見狀馬上把綁上繩的救生衣拋給他，但他愈飄愈遠捉不住救生衣，此時船的摩打又突然爆炸。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n身上只有T恤牛仔褲的莫克，情急下突然想起多年前看過美軍海豹突擊隊用長褲當救生衣的求生技巧。他憶述當時深深吸一口氣，設法脫下牛仔褲，然後將褲腳打結，舉出水面讓空氣灌入褲管，之後靠這件「臨時救生衣」等待救援，心裏一直想着家中10個月大的女兒。他形容脫褲時花了很大力氣，以為自己會死去。<br />\n<br />\n莫克的弟弟發出求救信號後，新西蘭海岸巡防隊和民間搜救公司出動直升機搜救，莫克漂浮3個多小時後終被發現救起。莫克感謝搜救人員，稱即使今次與死神擦肩，但仍然會出海，「我知道出海有風險，但我不會害怕，只是以後會更小心。」<br />\n<br />\n（新西蘭先驅報）"},{"pid":"0a14f9c4bb57543174d8da805a73e4c2fe3e5cd3","tid":1059934,"uid":86509,"like":1238,"dislike":54,"score":1184,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T12:27:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1955000/1958818/Titanic20171129_0007_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1955000%2F1958818%2FTitanic20171129_0007_1024.jpg&h=c28dc4c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿jack 根本唔使死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd4cc1fba84dcbe8a6e65b4d776c7b05db3ca525","tid":1059934,"uid":1654,"like":161,"dislike":4,"score":157,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T12:29:48.000Z","msg":"咁岩架船甩繩推左佢落海，<br />\n咁岩個細路又拋唔切水泡，<br />\n咁岩個摩打爆炸"},{"pid":"d544606daa0e4f215eb59d197cc5cb837db7880f","tid":1059934,"uid":86509,"like":560,"dislike":3,"score":557,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T12:30:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JUhZzWNcPKI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJUhZzWNcPKI&d=WTugOjWmLb2R3dS25JBA%2BdTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=8e29104e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JUhZzWNcPKI</a><br />\n<br />\n教埋你點整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4755ecf363ce4d8178dfa954d06e33fb839f00","tid":1059934,"uid":42188,"like":661,"dislike":2,"score":659,"quote":{"pid":"0a14f9c4bb57543174d8da805a73e4c2fe3e5cd3","tid":1059934,"uid":86509,"like":1238,"dislike":54,"score":1184,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T12:27:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1955000/1958818/Titanic20171129_0007_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1955000%2F1958818%2FTitanic20171129_0007_1024.jpg&h=c28dc4c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br 